---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Services - Inform Growth"
  description="We build revenue infrastructure that compounds. From diagnosis to AI-powered systems, everything we build is yours to own and scale."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="page-header section geo-grid">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header-content fade-up">
        <div class="header-eyebrow">Built For You</div>
        <h1>Your Revenue Engine, Compounding</h1>
        <p class="header-subtitle">
          We don't just consult - we build infrastructure that makes your team faster, smarter, and more autonomous every quarter. Everything we create is yours to own, maintain, and scale.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Approach: The 5-Step Process -->
  <section class="approach-section section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="approach-header fade-up">
        <h2>How We Work With You</h2>
        <p>A systematic approach that starts with understanding and ends with independence. Each step builds on the last, creating compounding value.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="approach-steps fade-up">
        <div class="approach-step">
          <div class="step-marker">01</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Explore</h3>
            <p class="step-for-you">We learn your business</p>
            <p>We audit your CRM, data architecture, and sales processes. We interview your team. We find where revenue is leaking and where opportunities are hiding.</p>
            <ul class="step-details">
              <li>Full system and process audit</li>
              <li>Stakeholder interviews</li>
              <li>Statistical analysis of your pipeline</li>
              <li>Gap identification and prioritization</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="approach-step">
          <div class="step-marker">02</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Codify</h3>
            <p class="step-for-you">We document your truth</p>
            <p>We define what your data means in your specific business context. Pipeline stages, ARR rules, field definitions - documented once, applied everywhere.</p>
            <ul class="step-details">
              <li>Business glossary and field registry</li>
              <li>Pipeline stage definitions</li>
              <li>Data validation rules</li>
              <li>Process documentation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="approach-step">
          <div class="step-marker">03</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Connect</h3>
            <p class="step-for-you">We integrate your tools</p>
            <p>One AI middleware layer connects your entire stack. HubSpot, Salesforce, Gong, Apollo, Clay - every tool feeds into one source of truth that your whole team can query.</p>
            <ul class="step-details">
              <li>API integrations and webhooks</li>
              <li>AI middleware deployment</li>
              <li>Real-time data synchronization</li>
              <li>Natural language query interface</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="approach-step">
          <div class="step-marker">04</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Empower</h3>
            <p class="step-for-you">We train your team</p>
            <p>We coach your revenue teams to leverage AI with their tools. Not just training - hands-on enablement that changes how they work every day.</p>
            <ul class="step-details">
              <li>Team workshops and training</li>
              <li>Custom playbooks and templates</li>
              <li>AI prompt libraries for your context</li>
              <li>Ongoing office hours and support</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="approach-step final">
          <div class="step-marker">05</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Compound</h3>
            <p class="step-for-you">Your system gets smarter</p>
            <p>Every question your team asks, every workflow that gets promoted to shared infrastructure, makes the next one faster and cheaper. The system learns what works.</p>
            <ul class="step-details">
              <li>New hires inherit full context</li>
              <li>New tools plug in automatically</li>
              <li>Best practices scale across teams</li>
              <li>Value accumulates over time</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Build: The AI Infrastructure -->
  <section class="infrastructure-section section bg-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="infra-header fade-up">
        <h2>The Infrastructure We Build For You</h2>
        <p>A governed AI layer that sits between your tools and your team. Read-only by default. Your credentials stay with you. Every integration reviewed before it goes live.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="infra-grid fade-up">
        <div class="infra-card">
          <div class="infra-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
              <path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>One Source of Truth</h3>
          <p>Your team asks questions in plain English. The AI queries your connected tools and returns answers in seconds - with the data definitions you've approved.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="infra-card">
          <div class="infra-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/>
              <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Read-Only by Default</h3>
          <p>The AI can read your systems to answer questions but cannot modify data unless explicitly approved. Your data stays safe.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="infra-card">
          <div class="infra-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Credentials Stay Local</h3>
          <p>Your API keys and sensitive credentials live on your infrastructure, not ours. We build the connections; you control the access.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="infra-card">
          <div class="infra-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M9 11l3 3L22 4"/>
              <path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>QA Review on Every Integration</h3>
          <p>Every tool we connect goes through automated and human review before it touches your production systems. No surprises.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="infra-card">
          <div class="infra-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
              <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/>
              <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Your Team Owns Everything</h3>
          <p>Every workflow, every integration, every definition lives in your infrastructure. We hand it back documented and ready for your team to maintain.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="infra-card">
          <div class="infra-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="10"/>
              <line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="4"/>
              <line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="16"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Costs Decrease Over Time</h3>
          <p>As workflows mature, expensive API calls become targeted queries. Your token costs go down as your context gets more precise.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="infra-cta fade-up">
        <a href="/security" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More About Our Security Model</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How We Work Together -->
  <section class="collab-section">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="collab-header fade-up">
        <h2>We work differently. <span class="collab-accent">(And that's on purpose.)</span></h2>
        <p>Our work is built through incremental steps and we apply our learnings throughout the process. We continuously incorporate your feedback to proactively solve problems. Our team can efficiently pivot alongside changing requirements, enabling us to spot challenges early.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Three Principles -->
      <div class="collab-principles fade-up">
        <div class="collab-principle">
          <div class="principle-icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Built through iteration.</h3>
          <p>We focus on rapid cycles to create real outcomes - not polished decks that sit in a drawer.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="collab-principle">
          <div class="principle-icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/>
              <path d="M12 1v4M12 19v4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Clear by design.</h3>
          <p>You get a single point of communication from start to finish. No handoffs. No surprises.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="collab-principle">
          <div class="principle-icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
              <path d="M3 21v-2a4 4 0 0 1 4-4h4a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v2"/>
              <circle cx="17" cy="11" r="3"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Powered by partnership.</h3>
          <p>Your team is part of the process. We build together, so you understand and own everything we create.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Progress > Perfection -->
      <div class="collab-progress fade-up">
        <div class="progress-left">
          <h3>Progress <span class="gt">&gt;</span> Perfection</h3>
          <p>We uncover what matters most to your business, craft and implement tailored solutions that iteratively bring your vision to life, and ensure you and your team gain lasting impact.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="progress-steps">
          <div class="progress-step">
            <div class="step-icon">
              <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/>
                <path d="M21 21l-4.35-4.35"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <span class="step-num">1.</span>
              <h4>Discover</h4>
              <p>We dig into your goals and challenges to uncover what drives real impact.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="progress-step">
            <div class="step-icon">
              <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path d="M12 19l7-7 3 3-7 7-3-3z"/>
                <path d="M18 13l-1.5-7.5L2 2l3.5 14.5L13 18l5-5z"/>
                <path d="M2 2l7.586 7.586"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <span class="step-num">2.</span>
              <h4>Design</h4>
              <p>We turn insights into clear strategies and actionable solutions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="progress-step">
            <div class="step-icon">
              <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <span class="step-num">3.</span>
              <h4>Develop</h4>
              <p>We bring ideas to life with precision, creativity, and technical know-how.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="progress-step">
            <div class="step-icon">
              <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/>
                <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <span class="step-num">4.</span>
              <h4>Deploy</h4>
              <p>We deliver seamless rollouts that set your team up for long-term success.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Service Tiers -->
  <section class="tiers-section section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="tiers-header fade-up">
        <h2>Three Ways to Start</h2>
        <p>Every engagement begins with understanding where you are. From there, we scope what makes sense for your team.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tiers-grid fade-up">
        <!-- Tier 1 -->
        <div class="tier-card">
          <div class="tier-label">Start Here</div>
          <h3>Revenue Diagnosis</h3>
          <p class="tier-desc">A full audit of your revenue infrastructure. We find what's broken, what's missing, and what's costing you money.</p>
          <div class="tier-guarantee">We find $100K+ in recoverable pipeline - or you don't pay.</div>
          <ul class="tier-includes">
            <li>CRM and data architecture review</li>
            <li>Sales process audit</li>
            <li>Pipeline leak analysis</li>
            <li>Prioritized repair roadmap</li>
            <li>30-minute debrief</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="tier-meta">
            <span class="tier-price">$1,500</span>
            <span class="tier-time">1-2 weeks</span>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Book Diagnosis</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Tier 2 -->
        <div class="tier-card featured">
          <div class="tier-label">Full Build</div>
          <h3>Revenue Engine Build</h3>
          <p class="tier-desc">We implement the full 5-step process. From diagnosis through to a connected, AI-powered revenue infrastructure your team owns.</p>
          <ul class="tier-includes">
            <li>Everything in Diagnosis</li>
            <li>Data cleanup and migration</li>
            <li>AI middleware deployment</li>
            <li>Tool integrations</li>
            <li>Team training and enablement</li>
            <li>Documentation and handoff</li>
            <li>30-day post-launch support</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="tier-meta">
            <span class="tier-price">$15K-$40K</span>
            <span class="tier-time">6-12 weeks</span>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Scope Your Build</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Tier 3 -->
        <div class="tier-card">
          <div class="tier-label">Ongoing</div>
          <h3>Revenue Assurance</h3>
          <p class="tier-desc">Continuous monitoring, optimization, and support. We keep your revenue engine running and help it compound over time.</p>
          <ul class="tier-includes">
            <li>24/7 system monitoring</li>
            <li>Monthly data quality reports</li>
            <li>Proactive issue resolution</li>
            <li>Quarterly strategic reviews</li>
            <li>Priority support</li>
            <li>New tool integrations</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="tier-meta">
            <span class="tier-price">$3K-$5K/mo</span>
            <span class="tier-time">Ongoing</span>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Get Assurance</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section class="final-cta section bg-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="final-cta-content fade-up">
        <h2>Ready to build a revenue engine that compounds?</h2>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Book a Meeting</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Page Header */
  .page-header {
    background-color: var(--navy);
    padding: var(--space-section) 0;
  }

  .header-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .header-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--sky-blue);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: white;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .header-subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: #8C8880;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Approach Section */
  .approach-section {
    background-color: var(--page-bg);
  }

  .approach-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .approach-header h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--heading-color);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .approach-header p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--muted-text);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .approach-steps {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .approach-step {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    background: var(--color-bg-raised);
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .approach-step:hover {
    border-color: var(--sky-blue);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(200, 240, 74, 0.1);
  }

  .approach-step.final {
    border-color: #C8F04A;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, white 0%, rgba(200, 240, 74, 0.03) 100%);
  }

  .approach-step.final:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(200, 240, 74, 0.15);
  }

  .step-marker {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--sky-blue);
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(200, 240, 74, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .approach-step.final .step-marker {
    color: #C8F04A;
    background: rgba(200, 240, 74, 0.1);
  }

  .step-content h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--heading-color);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .step-for-you {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--sky-blue);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .approach-step.final .step-for-you {
    color: #C8F04A;
  }

  .step-content > p:not(.step-for-you) {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--muted-text);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .step-details {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-xs) var(--space-lg);
  }

  .step-details li {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--muted-text);
    padding-left: var(--space-md);
    position: relative;
  }

  .step-details li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--sky-blue);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .approach-step.final .step-details li::before {
    color: #C8F04A;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .approach-step {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .step-marker {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
    }

    .step-details {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  /* Infrastructure Section */
  .infrastructure-section {
    background: #0D0D0B;
  }

  .bg-dark {
    background-color: var(--navy);
  }

  .infra-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .infra-header h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .infra-header p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: #8C8880;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .infra-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .infra-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .infra-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .infra-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .infra-card:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border-color: var(--sky-blue);
  }

  .infra-icon {
    color: var(--sky-blue);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .infra-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .infra-card p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: #8C8880;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .infra-cta {
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Collaboration Section */
  .collab-section {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--navy) 0%, var(--navy-light) 100%);
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .collab-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .collab-header {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .collab-header h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: white;
    line-height: 1.2;
